Enable/Disable Automatic Start on Boot
To Enable (starts every time it turns on):
bash
sudo systemctl enable voice_assistant.service
To Disable (stops starting at boot):
bash
sudo systemctl disable voice_assistant.service


🛠️ Manual Control (For right now)
Start the assistant now: sudo systemctl start voice_assistant.service
Stop the assistant now: sudo systemctl stop voice_assistant.service
Check if it's running: sudo systemctl status voice_assistant.service
Restart the assistant: sudo systemctl restart voice_assistant.service
